<title>USA: Chattem says to buy assets of Sunsource.</title>
<headline>Chattem says to buy assets of Sunsource.</headline>
<dateline>CHATTANOOGA, Tenn. 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Chattem Inc said Friday it agreed to buy the assets of Sunsource International Inc and an affiliated company, including the exclusive rights to five branded dietary supplement products.</p>
<p>Chattem said it expects the acquired brands will add incremental earings of $0.20 to $0.30 per share in the first full year of operations.</p>
<p>The company said, however, that for the balance of the year ending November 30, income from the brands will be only slightly accretive to per share earnings.</p>
<p>The purchase price on the deal was not disclosed.</p>
